a451b","tid":88924,"uid":24457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T07:58:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係我就讓位比佢之後係班女人面前暈低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n再唔係勉強D大聲咁話 &quot;伯伯你坐啦, 雖然我貧血易暈而家好唔舒服去緊睇醫生, 但係我都忍得住既&quot;<br />\n<br />\n咁樣呢D道德JJ先識收聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但個阿伯真係會坐 而其他人亦都唔會讓位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e659554706f11bb5c44307f36d63f4ee45841d","tid":88924,"uid":34482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:04:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次坐普通坐位 <br />\n條呀叔竟然話：後生都坐既<br />\n心諗唔通坐錯位？望望後面又唔係寫住關愛座<br />\n莫名其妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇俾錢牙屌你"},{"pid":"cfc6cba4788d6ca2e1b942609538d985002d9698","tid":88924,"uid":34482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:06:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係我就讓位比佢之後係班女人面前暈低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地都唔會讓，最多好人啲幫你屈其他人讓畀你"},{"pid":"c6085baeb579bc895ea128010560585b39827b98","tid":88924,"uid":39351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:15:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>後生=讓坐 乜撚野道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你咁睇係唔合理。<br />\n<br />\n但其實係咁樣derive出黎：<br />\n<br />\n1.後生=精力充沛<br />\n2.老人=無心無力<br />\n3.無心無力的人比精力充沛的人更需要關心，照顧。<br />\n4.讓座是其中一種關心，照顧他人的表現。<br />\n<br />\n所以，後生人需要讓座比老人。<br />\n<br />\n問題係 1. 同 2. 都係主要靠外表去分別，所以老人係佔優勢，因為視力佔左人嘅資訊接收 一個好重比例。"},{"pid":"4f08c46c9a448054eeb13e592662d45eee016927","tid":88924,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:17:52.000Z","msg":"最憎班偷拍狂，係屌就當面屌。成日就出帖批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />變態"},{"pid":"d801ac9ec6f9644e9451e0bcd8aeaaa98ac3eaa2","tid":88924,"uid":39351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:19:36.000Z","msg":"加上文化上，有尊重長輩呢個觀念。<br />\n<br />\n政府係on99，用錯方法。要推行尊重長輩呢個觀念有大把方法，但係都要用讓座標籤呢個方法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388b9ca361b6c4d71226612b27aea8dd7ca9cc90","tid":88924,"uid":8422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:22:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最憎班偷拍狂，係屌就當面屌。成日就出帖批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />變態</blockquote><br />\n呢個真啲廢老唔夠人講淨係識影人擺上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1829b44a19be9132392abb20e375468a98c1d2da","tid":88924,"uid":25945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:24:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加上文化上，有尊重長輩呢個觀念。<br />\n<br />\n政府係on99，用錯方法。要推行尊重長輩呢個觀念有大把方法，但係都要用讓座標籤呢個方法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係D on9仔係咁批鬥 政府先開始搞呢D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863ca0053a98776356008d6355adff151b3c7e2a","tid":88924,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:26:06.000Z","msg":"洗乜理人地點睇 坐咪坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4540496d5caecbba68e75120fc2d89c89bea0167","tid":88924,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:27:43.000Z","msg":"我都好懦弱唔敢鬧返人 所以平時點都唔會坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}